by stopping the ball rotation as much as possible.

134
00:08:14,126 --> 00:08:19,493
The basic knuckleball is thrown by putting your
index and middle fingers against the ball like this.

135
00:08:19,566 --> 00:08:24,652
How you grip a fastball makes it spin and it doesn't
allow it to wobble around like a knuckleball does.

136
00:08:24,677 --> 00:08:26,042
