137
00:08:26,288 --> 00:08:27,207
I get it now.

138
00:08:27,232 --> 00:08:31,144
He's using telekinesis to move the ball
around after he's thrown it, isn't he?

139
00:08:31,191 --> 00:08:31,819
Yes.

140
00:08:31,956 --> 00:08:34,581
Wow! That's amazing, right?

141
00:08:34,652 --> 00:08:36,470
Does she get any of this?

142
00:08:36,819 --> 00:08:40,475
It will be bad if we can't get ahold
of him before the national championship.

143
00:08:40,866 --> 00:08:42,184
Let's head there right now.

144
00:08:42,462 --> 00:08:44,087
Well, what about class?

145
00:08:44,112 --> 00:08:48,119
It's all right. No matter how we act, as
long as we're a part of the student council,

146
00:08:48,144 --> 00:08:51,585
there can be no demerits towards
our grades or our school reports.

147
00:08:51,966 --> 00:08:53,205
Is that so?

148
00:08:53,816 --> 00:08:56,466
We're from the Hoshinoumi Academy Student Council.

149
00:08:56,681 --> 00:08:59,371
