and listen to what I have to say, please?

153
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,754
What is it?

154
00:09:07,341 --> 00:09:09,228
I'm not beating around the bush here.

155
00:09:09,331 --> 00:09:13,172
Do you use telekinesis to control
your knuckleballs after you throw them?

156
00:09:14,156 --> 00:09:17,292
Telekinesis? As in supernatural abilities?

157
00:09:17,467 --> 00:09:19,260
Are you insane? Of course I don't.

158
00:09:19,285 --> 00:09:22,442
Are you from some occult research
club instead of the student council?

159
00:09:22,467 --> 00:09:24,885
All right, wise guy, listen closely.

160
00:09:24,980 --> 00:09:28,845
That power of yours is like a disease
that's only around during your adolescence.

161
00:09:29,091 --> 00:09:31,304
